<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Lal Pathien Na kawmah kipah thu ka gen ui,
 Na lungsietna'n nei na enkawl in nei pui khawm hi;
 Thisan zieka unau mun tin, gamtina mite,
 Na min pakcha leh chawian dingin ka kikhawm ui.

[V2]
 Ka kikhawppi nau hi (2)
 Aw Lalpa nangin vang hun pien la,
 Na min lopina dingin;
 Na Thagau Thiengtho in ei pawl zingin.

[V3]
 2. Ka vaihawmteu hi Nangin hun panpih zing inla,
 Na gam let na'nga kitup taka vaihawm dingin;
 Amau leh a lawiteu chung ale chingthei taka,
 Vaihawm dingin chitna leh lemhet na'n hun thuomin.

[V4]
 3. Thagau a dingin vangsakna ka muhna dingun,
 Na chanchin Pha gente Nangin hun panpih inla;
 Hinna thak, hatna thak, kipahna thak mu dingin,
 Aw nang ngeiin Na chanchin Pha hun phuongin ka tiu.

[V5]
 4. Aw Lalpa, Pathien ka ngetnau Na kawm tung henla,
 Na mina hung kikhawm na lungsiet-Na mite hin;
 Ka hatnau, ka thiemnau ka hun pieu na gam letna,
 Dingin Na vangpieknan ei hun vukin, Aw Lalpa.</lyrics>
<title>Thagau Thiengtho Chielna</title>
</song>